#: ../../source/language/java/framework.rst:9
msgid ""
"Servlet(Server Applet)是Java "
"Servlet的简称，称为小服务程序或服务连接器，是用Java编写的服务器端程序，主要功能在于交互式地浏览和修改数据，生成动态Web内容。"
msgstr ""
"Servlet (Server Applet) is short for Java Servlet. It is also called a small "
"service program or service connector. A Servlet is a server-side program "
"written in Java whose main function is to interactively browse and modify "
"data and generate dynamic Web content."

#: ../../source/language/java/framework.rst:11
msgid "狭义的Servlet是指Java语言实现的一个接口，广义的Servlet是指任何实现了这个Servlet接口的类，一般情况下，人们将Servlet理解为后者。Servlet运行于支持Java的应用服务器中。从原理上讲，Servlet可以响应任何类型的请求，但绝大多数情况下Servlet只用来扩展基于HTTP协议的Web服务器。"
msgstr "In the narrow sense, Servlet refers to an interface implemented in the Java language. In the broad sense, Servlet refers to any class that implements this Servlet interface; in practice, people usually mean the latter. Servlets run in Java-capable application servers. In principle, a Servlet can respond to any type of request, but in most cases Servlets are used only to extend HTTP-based Web servers."

#: ../../source/language/java/framework.rst:14
msgid "生命周期为"
msgstr "The lifecycle is"

#: ../../source/language/java/framework.rst:15
msgid "客户端请求该 Servlet"
msgstr "The client requests the Servlet"

#: ../../source/language/java/framework.rst:16
msgid "加载 Servlet 类到内存"
msgstr "Load the Servlet class into memory"

#: ../../source/language/java/framework.rst:17
msgid "实例化并调用init()方法初始化该 Servlet"
msgstr "Instantiate it and call the init() method to initialize the Servlet"

#: ../../source/language/java/framework.rst:18
msgid "service()(根据请求方法不同调用 ``doGet()`` / ``doPost()`` / ... / ``destroy()``"
msgstr "service() calls ``doGet()`` / ``doPost()`` / ... / ``destroy()`` depending on the request method"

#: ../../source/language/java/framework.rst:21
msgid "接口"
msgstr "Interfaces"

#: ../../source/language/java/framework.rst:23
msgid "``init()``"
msgstr "``init()``"

#: ../../source/language/java/framework.rst:25
msgid "在 Servlet 的生命期中，仅执行一次 init() 方法，在服务器装入 Servlet 时执行。"
msgstr "During a Servlet's lifecycle, the init() method is executed only once, when the server loads the Servlet."

#: ../../source/language/java/framework.rst:27
msgid "``service()``"
msgstr "``service()``"

#: ../../source/language/java/framework.rst:29
msgid ""
"service() 方法是 Servlet 的核心。每当一个客户请求一个HttpServlet对象，该对象的 ``service()`` "
"方法就要被调用，而且传递给这个方法一个\"请求\"(ServletRequest)对象和一个\"响应\"(ServletResponse)对象作为参数。"
msgstr ""
"The service() method is the core of a Servlet. Whenever a client requests an "
"HttpServlet object, the object's ``service()`` method is called, with a "
"\"request\" (ServletRequest) object and a \"response\" (ServletResponse) "
"object passed as parameters."

#: ../../source/language/java/framework.rst:32
msgid "Struts 2"
msgstr "Struts 2"

#: ../../source/language/java/framework.rst:36
msgid "Struts2是一个基于MVC设计模式的Web应用框架，它本质上相当于一个servlet，在MVC设计模式中，Struts2作为控制器(Controller)来建立模型与视图的数据交互。"
msgstr "Struts2 is a Web application framework based on the MVC design pattern. It is essentially equivalent to a servlet. In the MVC design pattern, Struts2 acts as the Controller to establish data interaction between the model and the view."

#: ../../source/language/java/framework.rst:39
#: ../../source/language/java/framework.rst:81
msgid "请求流程"
msgstr "Request Flow"

#: ../../source/language/java/framework.rst:40
msgid "客户端发送请求的tomcat服务器"
msgstr "The client sends a request to the Tomcat server"

#: ../../source/language/java/framework.rst:41
msgid "请求经过一系列过滤器"
msgstr "The request passes through a series of filters"

#: ../../source/language/java/framework.rst:42
msgid "FilterDispatcher调用ActionMapper来决定这个请求是否要调用某个Action"
msgstr "FilterDispatcher calls ActionMapper to determine whether this request should call an Action"

#: ../../source/language/java/framework.rst:43
msgid "ActionMppaer决定调用某个ActionFilterDispatcher把请求给ActionProxy"
msgstr "ActionMppaer decides to call an Action, and FilterDispatcher passes the request to ActionProxy"

#: ../../source/language/java/framework.rst:44
msgid "ActionProxy通过Configuration Manager查看structs.xml，找到对应的Action类"
msgstr "ActionProxy uses Configuration Manager to inspect structs.xml and find the corresponding Action class"

#: ../../source/language/java/framework.rst:45
msgid "ActionProxy创建一个ActionInvocation对象"
msgstr "ActionProxy creates an ActionInvocation object"

#: ../../source/language/java/framework.rst:46
msgid "ActionInvocation对象回调Action的execute方法"
msgstr "The ActionInvocation object calls back the Action's execute method"

#: ../../source/language/java/framework.rst:47
msgid "Action执行完毕后，ActionInvocation根据返回的字符串，找到相应的result，通过HttpServletResponse返回给服务器"
msgstr "After the Action finishes, ActionInvocation finds the corresponding result based on the returned string and returns it to the server through HttpServletResponse"

