#: ../../source/language/java/framework.rst:141
msgid ""
"Apache Shiro "
"1.6.0之前的版本，由于Shiro拦截器与requestURI的匹配流程与Web框架的拦截器的匹配流程有差异，攻击者构造一个特殊的http请求，可以绕过Shiro的认证，未授权访问敏感路径。"
msgstr "In Apache Shiro versions before 1.6.0, the matching process between the Shiro interceptor and requestURI differs from the matching process used by Web framework interceptors. An attacker can craft a special http request to bypass Shiro authentication and access sensitive paths without authorization."

#: ../../source/language/java/framework.rst:145
msgid ""
"Apache Shiro "
"1.5.3之前的版本，由于Shiro拦截器与requestURI的匹配流程与Web框架的拦截器的匹配流程有差异，攻击者构造一个特殊的http请求，可以绕过Shiro的认证，未授权访问敏感路径。此漏洞存在两种攻击方式。"
msgstr "In Apache Shiro versions before 1.5.3, the matching process between the Shiro interceptor and requestURI differs from the matching process used by Web framework interceptors. An attacker can craft a special http request to bypass Shiro authentication and access sensitive paths without authorization. This vulnerability has two attack methods."

#: ../../source/language/java/framework.rst:149
msgid ""
"Apache Shiro "
"1.5.2之前的版本，由于Shiro拦截器与requestURI的匹配流程与Web框架的拦截器的匹配流程有差异，攻击者构造一个特殊的http请求，可以绕过Shiro的认证，未授权访问敏感路径。"
msgstr "In Apache Shiro versions before 1.5.2, the matching process between the Shiro interceptor and requestURI differs from the matching process used by Web framework interceptors. An attacker can craft a special http request to bypass Shiro authentication and access sensitive paths without authorization."

#: ../../source/language/java/framework.rst:153
msgid ""
"Apache Shiro 1.4.2之前的版本默认使用 ``AES/CBC/PKCS5Padding`` "
"模式加密,开启RememberMe功能的Shiro组件将允许远程攻击者构造序列化数据，通过Padding Oracle "
"Attack进行爆破，即使在秘钥未知的条件下，也可以在目标服务器上执行任意命令。"
msgstr "Apache Shiro versions before 1.4.2 use ``AES/CBC/PKCS5Padding`` mode encryption by default. A Shiro component with RememberMe enabled allows a remote attacker to construct serialized data and brute force it through a Padding Oracle Attack, enabling arbitrary command execution on the target server even when the key is unknown."

#: ../../source/language/java/framework.rst:157
msgid ""
"Apache Shiro 1.2.5之前的版本在 "
"``org.apache.shiro.mgt.AbstractRememberMeManager`` 中存在AES默认秘钥 "
"``kPH+bIxk5D2deZiIxcaaaA==`` "
"，开启RememberMe功能的Shiro组件将允许远程攻击者构造序列化数据，在目标服务器上执行任意命令。"
msgstr "Apache Shiro versions before 1.2.5 have the default AES key ``kPH+bIxk5D2deZiIxcaaaA==`` in ``org.apache.shiro.mgt.AbstractRememberMeManager``. A Shiro component with RememberMe enabled allows a remote attacker to construct serialized data and execute arbitrary commands on the target server."
